  "detailed_description": "After many years of learning the art of magic, young magician Martin has to pass all the challenges to prove that he is worthy to possess the power of the magic staff. To make it come true, he has to put the pommel of his magic staff into the waters of the magical lake located in the deepest part of the ancient castle. <br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful graphics in the pixel art style<br></li><li>Ambient music in retro style<br></li><li>Challenging and complex puzzles<br></li><li>The retro atmosphere of the game</li></ul>",
